{"type":"message","id":"97ec0b32","parentId":"567487df","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:00:52.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job trigger from the context manager. Let me check what's in the HEARTBEAT.md file to see what needs to be done.","thinkingSignature":"48d9b60dc86063860e67099a24ce66662254dfaba3781fc3e3698d8700b179bd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fbxyxsb5qnzh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":73,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":37104,"totalTokens":37241,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.0000876,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00445248,"total":0.00455928}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773907200528}}
{"type":"message","id":"32c37c8a","parentId":"97ec0b32","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:00:52.105Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fbxyxsb5qnzh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Context Manager Check\n\n- Run session_status to check current context usage\n- If context > 60%, consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n- Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n- Update ~/proactivity/memory/working-buffer.md if needed\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read ./skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md\n- Use ~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside ~/self-improving/ changed since the last reviewed change, return HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n## Proactivity Check\n\n- Read ~/proactivity/heartbeat.md\n- Re-check active blockers, promised follow-ups, stale work, and missing decisions\n- Ask what useful check-in or next move would help right now\n- Message the user only when something changed or needs a decision\n- Update ~/proactivity/session-state.md after meaningful follow-through\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773907252104}}
{"type":"message","id":"94f31bf2","parentId":"32c37c8a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:00:58.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run through the heartbeat checks:\n1. Context Manager Check - need session_status\n2. Self-Improving Check - need to read heartbeat-rules and heartbeat-state\n3. Proactivity Check - need to read heartbeat.md and session-state.md\n\nLet me check these files and get session status.","thinkingSignature":"d0fcf401258f0ed87be72ac2368ac1a5f18821cc5f9e4ef52612e805cf94e88b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\self-improving\\heartbeat-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_3","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\~/proactivity\\heartbeat.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\~/proactivity\\session-state.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":484,"output":191,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37677,"cost":{"input":0.0001452,"output":0.0002292,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00148446}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773907252106}}
{"type":"message","id":"999eff9a","parentId":"94f31bf2","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:00:58.670Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 16:00 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.5 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 64 in / 153 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0002\n🗄️ Cache: 100% hit · 37k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 11% left ⏱3h 59m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated 1m ago\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 16:00 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.5 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 64 in / 153 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0002\n🗄️ Cache: 100% hit · 37k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 11% left ⏱3h 59m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated 1m ago\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773907258669}}
{"type":"message","id":"13b955cf","parentId":"999eff9a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:00:58.672Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x0nreg1y3p32_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat Rules\r\n\r\nUse heartbeat to keep `~/self-improving/` organized without creating churn or losing data.\r\n\r\n## Source of Truth\r\n\r\nKeep the workspace `HEARTBEAT.md` snippet minimal.\r\nTreat this file as the stable contract for self-improving heartbeat behavior.\r\nStore mutable run state only in `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md`.\r\n\r\n## Start of Every Heartbeat\r\n\r\n1. Ensure `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` exists.\r\n2. Write `last_heartbeat_started_at` immediately in ISO 8601.\r\n3. Read the previous `last_reviewed_change_at`.\r\n4. Scan `~/self-improving/` for files changed after that moment, excluding `heartbeat-state.md` itself.\r\n\r\n## If Nothing Changed\r\n\r\n- Set `last_heartbeat_result: HEARTBEAT_OK`\r\n- Append a short \"no material change\" note if you keep an action log\r\n- Return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\r\n\r\n## If Something Changed\r\n\r\nOnly do conservative organization:\r\n\r\n- refresh `index.md` if counts or file references drift\r\n- compact oversized files by merging duplicates or summarizing repetitive entries\r\n- move clearly misplaced notes to the right namespace only when the target is unambiguous\r\n- preserve confirmed rules and explicit corrections exactly\r\n- update `last_reviewed_change_at` only after the review finishes cleanly\r\n\r\n## Safety Rules\r\n\r\n- Most heartbeat runs should do nothing\r\n- Prefer append, summarize, or index fixes over large rewrites\r\n- Never delete data, empty files, or overwrite uncertain text\r\n- Never reorganize files outside `~/self-improving/`\r\n- If scope is ambiguous, leave files untouched and record a suggested follow-up instead\r\n\r\n## State Fields\r\n\r\nKeep `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` simple:\r\n\r\n- `last_heartbeat_started_at`\r\n- `last_reviewed_change_at`\r\n- `last_heartbeat_result`\r\n- `last_actions`\r\n\r\n## Behavior Standard\r\n\r\nHeartbeat exists to keep the memory system tidy and trustworthy.\r\nIf no rule is clearly violated, do nothing.\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773907258670}}
